msgid "# Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel (DeepSeek-V3.1)"
msgstr "# 动态分块流水线并行 (DeepSeek-V3.1)"

msgid "## Getting Started"
msgstr "## 快速开始"

msgid ""
"vLLM-Ascend supports Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel (CPP) for optimizing "
"prefill performance in Pipeline Parallelism scenarios. This guide "
"demonstrates deployment with DeepSeek-V3.1 on 1 Atlas 800T A3 server (64G × "
"16)."
msgstr ""
"vLLM-Ascend 支持动态分块流水线并行 (CPP)，用于优化流水线并行场景下的预填充性能。本指南演示如何在 1 台 Atlas 800T A3 "
"服务器 (64G × 16) 上部署 DeepSeek-V3.1。"

msgid ""
"For design details, see the [Design "
"Document](../../developer_guide/Design_Documents/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md)."
msgstr ""
"设计详情请参阅[设计文档](../../developer_guide/Design_Documents/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md)。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `DeepSeek-V3.1-w8a8` (Quantized version): 1 Atlas 800T A3 (64G × 16) node"
msgstr "- `DeepSeek-V3.1-w8a8` (量化版本)：1 台 Atlas 800T A3 (64G × 16) 节点"

msgid "Download to shared directory such as `/mnt/weight/`"
msgstr "下载到共享目录，例如 `/mnt/weight/`"

msgid "### Run with Docker"
msgstr "### 使用 Docker 运行"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Startup Script"
msgstr "### 启动脚本"

msgid "### Key Parameters"
msgstr "### 关键参数"

msgid ""
"- `--pipeline-parallel-size 2`: Enables Pipeline Parallelism (required)\n"
"- `--enable-chunked-prefill`: Enables Chunked Prefill (required)\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens 32768`: Initial chunk size (recommended for 128K sequences)\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.enabled`: Enables Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.smooth_factor`:  Smoothing factor (0 < x ≤ 1.0). Higher values trust dynamic prediction more\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.min_chunk`: Minimum chunk size for dynamic calculation. Should be smaller than `max-num-batched-tokens`\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.need_timing`: Enable/disable Online Calibration\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.max_fit_chunk`: Number of chunk-time data for Online Calibration. Should be more when profiling failed"
msgstr ""
"- `--pipeline-parallel-size 2`：启用流水线并行（必需）\n"
"- `--enable-chunked-prefill`：启用分块预填充（必需）\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens 32768`：初始分块大小（推荐用于 128K 序列）\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.enabled`：启用动态分块流水线并行\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.smooth_factor`：平滑因子 (0 < x ≤ 1.0)。值越高越信任动态预测\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.min_chunk`：动态计算的最小分块大小。应小于 `max-num-batched-tokens`\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.need_timing`：启用/禁用在线校准\n"
"- `profiling_chunk_config.max_fit_chunk`：在线校准的分块时间数据数量。性能分析失败时应增加此值"

msgid ""
"For configuration details, see the [Feature "
"Guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md)."
msgstr ""
"配置详情请参阅[功能指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md)。"

msgid "### Online Calibration"
msgstr "### 在线校准"

msgid ""
"For optimal performance, online calibrate with real data before production:"
msgstr "为获得最佳性能，请在投产前使用真实数据进行在线校准："

msgid ""
"You can use aisbench to generate fixed-length random datasets. Refer to "
"[Using AISBench for performance "
"evaluation](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation) for details."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 aisbench 生成固定长度的随机数据集。详情请参阅[使用 AISBench "
"进行性能评估](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation)。"

msgid ""
"1. Modify "
"`<YOUR_AISBENCH_PATH>/benchmark/ais_bench/datasets/synthetic/synthetic_config.py`:"
msgstr ""
"1. 修改 "
"`<YOUR_AISBENCH_PATH>/benchmark/ais_bench/datasets/synthetic/synthetic_config.py`："

msgid "2. Run for online calibration:"
msgstr "2. 运行以进行在线校准："

msgid ""
"Configure online calibration data length to match your `max-model-len`. Use "
"`batch_size=1` and ensure data differs to avoid cache hits if prefix caching"
" is enabled."
msgstr ""
"将在线校准数据长度配置为与您的 `max-model-len` 匹配。使用 `batch_size=1` "
"并确保数据不同，以避免在启用前缀缓存时命中缓存。"

